Margaret Whiting (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Whiting_(actress) 0 Margaret Whiting (born 1932) is a British film and television actress. She was nominated in 1978 for a Saturn Award as "Best Supporting Actress" in Sinbad and the Eye of the Tiger. She is an alumna and Associate Member of RADA.
